A  31-year-old man, Edidiong Pius Ototi has been sentenced to death by hanging, for killing his father, late Mr. Pius David Ototi, whom he accused of being a Warlock. The judgment delivered by the Akwa Ibom State High Court sitting in Ikot Ekpene, presided over by Justice Augustine Odokwo, found Ototi guilty of murder, which is punishable by death, under section 326 (1) of the Criminal Code, Laws of Akwa Ibom State 2000. Dressed in black with a Sentence Cap, the Judge held that Ototi be hanged by the neck until he dies, praying God to have mercy upon his soul. HOW NIGERIAN MEN CAN NOW NATURALLY STOP PREMATURE EJACULATION, LOW SPERM COUNT AND OTHER MEN'S SEXUAL NEEDS. MADAM ALWAYS WANTS IT BIGGER, STRONGER AND LONG-LASTING!!! The judge expressed satisfaction that  the prosecution team from the State Ministry of Justice had proven the case beyond reasonable doubt that the accused committed the offense. Daily Independent reports that the condemned Edidiong Ototi, a native of Ikot Akwa in Obot Akara Local Government Area, had admitted in his confessional statement at the Police Headquarters, Ikot Akpan Abia, that he killed and buried his father in a pit toilet on November 18, 2018. FG Using FTZs To Reduce High Unemployment Rate, Insecurity BREAKING: [Video] Ogun Receives 100,000 Dozes Of COVID-19 Vaccines In an hour-long judgment, Justice Odokwo said. Ototi had no right under the law to take the life of his 60-year-old father, whom he accused of being responsible for the untimely death of his two grandchildren.